Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.68,0:01:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类因人口膨胀而向宇宙移民已过了半个世纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周围漂浮着巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为人类的“第二故乡”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.04,0:01:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们就在这里出生、成长、生儿育女\N并走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世纪0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.62,0:02:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离地球最远的宇宙都市SIDE 3\N以ZION公国之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.00,0:02:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球联邦政府发起了独立战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在开始一个月的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.59,0:02:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国和地球联邦军有半数以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们对于自己的行为产生了恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘逃离月神二号作战’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巡洋舰 玛达加斯加号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.42,0:02:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入港基准速度左舷2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方向正确！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,White Base已经入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各人员马上回岗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武器填充组立即集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总务人员请问在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做好接待母舰的准备没有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切准备妥当！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各人员在母舰停泊后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上做整备工作！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.48,0:03:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母舰上有一百个以上的百姓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为SIDE 7号受袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会到来月神二号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想收容他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是月神二号也在一级戒备状态下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,几经艰苦才来到的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.63,0:03:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然不肯收留我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎会有这种事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于你这个问题，让我来回答！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是月神二号基地司令马健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.31,0:03:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是布莱特君？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.24,0:03:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民们非常疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你们可以收容舰上全部人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一直在逃避ZION军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就没好好休息过！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里没有多余地方去收留百姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没可能吧...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我要各位留在此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等待地球联邦军有指示后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.91,0:04:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才可安排大家返回地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.24,0:04:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎么行...？想回去啊...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我宣布的人名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要和其它难民隔开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特·诺亚、米莱·八洲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良·保政，雪拉·玛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯·西登、隼人·小林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗·雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么！把哥哥们怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请告诉我这是什么意思...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仕官侯补生和平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.57,0:04:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自使用军队秘密武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是指使用White Base和GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.58,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们准备会受到军事审判吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,White Base没收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM将受到封闭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,归回我们军队管理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连当时SIDE 7号是状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不去查清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然向我们说这番说话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是司令官，马健！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.88,0:05:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你收留母舰及百姓们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会处理一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请安心在此养伤吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待会封好GUNDAM就轮到钢坦克了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢坦克怎处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙已经损坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快做吧！否则司令又要骂了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION军会来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.03,0:06:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那‘红色彗星’夏亚绝对不会放弃追踪母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如封闭了GUNDAM的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.92,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没资格和我说战略的问题！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本不知道‘红色彗星’的利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的不是正规军人的判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才觉这样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过‘红色彗星’这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个有名的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是不会做以一只姆沙尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便来挑战我们月神二号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种愚蠢行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们似乎仍未被雷达深测到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.97,0:06:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一带的米诸夫斯基粒子很浓厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人就在附近居然仍未探出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现代战争发展到某个阶段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能又会回复到古时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面对面那种接近战也说不定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你想毁灭月神二号？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.75,0:07:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉，你会赞成吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月神二号是拥有庞大建设的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军事家的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不会相信会以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这姆沙尔级战舰去攻击的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们才去攻击他们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是有对策的，杜力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝你成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时的那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是十年前失散了的妹妹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如是亚路佩西雅的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她太勇敢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再动的话我便开枪了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.28,0:08:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚路佩西雅是个很温柔的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用太空服潜入敌军基地！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一个目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夺取联邦军的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二个目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.43,0:08:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要夺取那艘母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如失败的话就要破坏它们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.78,0:08:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饭来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我要见马健司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你怎么该也是没用的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能肯定夏亚一定不会来袭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话虽如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不先填饱肚子不成啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有得吃时不吃饱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有事时什么也做不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯说得对，阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃饭就像子弹放入枪膛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为一个士兵，就算不想吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也必须要吃下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，开始行动吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.19,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先别急，你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红外线探测器..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心些装上爆雷别碰到它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.36,0:10:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我绝不能忘记这双层构造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是和ZION的ZAKU决定性分别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.93,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...GUNDAM最优胜的是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是战斗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和一向的ZAKU不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.47,0:11:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次的战斗过程均记录下来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连战斗过程也可记录？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换句话说GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愈作战得多就愈学会作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变得更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错！而且连我这个生手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.12,0:11:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可和身经百战的夏亚打个平手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并不关乎我的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是GUNDAM的教育型计算机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性能太优越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太谦虚了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重力装置坏了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.85,0:11:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来电源部份被毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们竟偷越过了监视雷达网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令！相信敌人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿太空服的特殊破坏部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和布莱特所说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令马剑号出击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快开门！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.80,0:12:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道他们忘了我们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可等在这里下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,门开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.68,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电源终止连电子锁也失灵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！米莱和雪拉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该在隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱、雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马剑号立即出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开稳定锁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION军已开始攻击这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.01,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何不让我们到安全地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为司令还未有命令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这岂不是叫我们等死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！我不是这个意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那请你通知司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他想法子吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令现在根本没时间理会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在干么，快过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快叫大家集合！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将White Base驶离军港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗解除GUNDAM封印！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.90,0:13:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马剑号出来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好...中伏了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马剑号将出入口塞住？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发动引擎，准备出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良、凯、阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解开GUNDAM封印了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.40,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别心急，才刚开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，难民呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚从重力区正过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳·波正在带领住他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！我现在先去GUNDAM那里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱！待大引擎有足够动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便微速前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令 你没事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.43,0:15:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过擦伤一点罢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁把White Base开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驶过去！靠近White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在这里干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经下了命令要封闭它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.79,0:16:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够和夏亚作战的只有GUNDAM！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我命令你立即离开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我预了要背上叛逆罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马健司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的敌人应该是ZION军吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是我们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们没时间向你说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.28,0:16:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军队内军纪的重要性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上级的命令是绝对不可违背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军纪   军纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.79,0:16:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有又如何！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军人为守军法要死是你们的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.02,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以叫百姓陪你一起送死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马健司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.76,0:16:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马健君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.83,0:16:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听我说，马健君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论是White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有GUNDAM，钢坦克和钢加农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也都是联邦的秘密武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在唯有说，最不幸的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们用得比我们熟练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.16,0:17:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且已经有两次的作战经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...舰长...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.30,0:17:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，他们都是外行人..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你身为司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有责任帮助他们作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会负上责任的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会听舰长你的吩咐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.07,0:18:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马殊，希司，你们听着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.51,0:18:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要潜入去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.81,0:18:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口气将木马型战舰及机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.58,0:18:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部破坏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.75,0:18:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马健司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不移开马剑号的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母舰是不可能出港的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去，未作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有的战舰也会覆没！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是姆沙尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,击沉马剑号吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.44,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把母舰固定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,预备防爆措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.54,0:19:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备母舰主炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下防爆罩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄准马剑号内的反应炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家做好冲击的防卫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，快离开港口通道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是个怎样的人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长，我们成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.32,0:21:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.12,0:21:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起码在回地球前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就交给他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是舰长的遗愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.43,0:21:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在和ZION军交战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.60,0:22:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上困难重重时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.40,0:22:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,值得让我们学习的前辈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.21,0:22:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却相继离我们而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.74,0:22:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不觉得这是个冷酷的时代吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.46,0:22:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长，你的White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.20,0:22:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一定会亲手送回地球的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.09,0:22:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.49,0:23:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.04,0:23:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果随着重力坠落就会燃烧殆尽的大气圈突入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这瞬间夏亚对White Base发动奇袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.69,0:23:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌我双方都处于危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否都能活着看到大地呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.55,0:23:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 ‘进入大气层’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.26,0:23:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够存活下去吗？

